					<h2 class="main--heading">AN ENVIRONMENT DESIGNED <br>ESPECIALLY FOR YOU </h2>
					<p>Do you ever find your phone ringing while you are treating a customer? As a salon owner or salon employee, you spend a lot of time on the phone with the customers who call you to make an appointment. Many of these calls are made when you are in the middle of treatment and your current client deserves your absolute attention. Mi Salon offers the solution for this. We focus on both the salon and the client's planning by automating this process for you. Mi Salon has been developed to help you manage your salon more effectively and easily. Efficiency and user-friendliness are therefore central to us. We have developed an environment in which you can manage all your appointments easily and clearly.</p>
